; L part — Step 15 γ proof 対象、 melody part 内 \c inline (= R command CYM semantics)、 cr = \c + r(rest) fixture pattern (= NOT "CYM" abbreviation、 NOT related to sample symbol name "top")
; PMDDotNET emit 期待: L part body bytecode = 0xEB 0x04 (+ 0x80 part end)
; driver pmdneo_part_main → commandsp(0xEB) → commandsp_rhykey → pmdneo_rhythm_event_trigger → bit 2 → _rhythm_event_cym_trigger → ADPCM-A L ch CYM trigger (= adpcma_sample_top reuse)
; ADR-0029 §決定 3 / 軸 1: CYM sample source = existing adpcma_sample_top symbol reuse (= 「top」 = sample provenance 名 / 「CYM」 = PMD semantics 名 wording 分離、 alias 新設なし)
